    "en": {
      "title": "Power cut schedule for July 4, 5",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Public Utilities Commission of Sri Lanka announced today (03) that permission has been granted to implement a 3-hour power cut tomorrow (04) and the day after tomorrow (05) as requested by the Sri Lanka Electricity Board.",
        "Accordingly, the commission has announced that power cut will be implemented for 1 hour and 40 minutes during the day and 1 hour and 20 minutes during the night in 20 zones from A to W.",
        "The commission has announced that 2 hours and 30 minutes of power cut will be implemented in CSE zones from 6 am to 8.30 am, and 3 hours power cut will be enforced from 5.30 am to 8 am in MNOX, Y and Z zones."
      ],
